-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=9052eb71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=dcccd9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=947aef02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=f762edfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b7e51808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d196eb13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=88223482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=965f0302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n<br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4c41c52e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=0cae1002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=721b67db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e6d231f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhk.nextmedia%2Fvideos%2F2433207320290299%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=57bae514\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/2433207320290299/</a><br />\n黑警用催淚彈直射向記者<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=610e37b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n[上環 7.21] 蘋果影到有義士訓低咗，綠衫圍著 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FApplePhotographers%2Fphotos%2Fa.1131233677080155%2F1131269430409913%3Ftype%3D3%26sfns%3Dmo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=369fb882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ApplePhotographers/photos/a.1131233677080155/1131269430409913?type=3&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n（07.21）譴責警察暴力：記者被催淚彈打中，係直接打中！<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcTeVHAuMLP4%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=610e37b8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cTeVHAuMLP4&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n7.21民陣大遊行 | 警方平射角度開槍清場<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEsy4jTTOpYI%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=c300ef1e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Esy4jTTOpYI&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n有記者直接被催淚彈打中<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FcTeVHAuMLP4&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=3eddff47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/cTeVHAuMLP4</a><br />\n有義士腳部中槍 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F105259197447%2Fposts%2F10157863977222448%3Fs%3D1279554103%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dmo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=2f4c92eb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/105259197447/posts/10157863977222448?s=1279554103&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n【2225 上環】警方施放多枚催淚彈，其後多部警車在警察防線後方鳴笛 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2513792761974182&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a1c5d9ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2513792761974182</a><br />\n7.21 催淚彈在人群中爆開 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D446725156177245&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=7ddd7600\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=446725156177245</a><br />\n7.21 無證速龍向記者舉槍 亮警棍威嚇 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D370689103642714&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=9d72cdac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=370689103642714</a><br />\n7.21 警察開槍射胡椒彈 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D320505138857250&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=bc26c933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=320505138857250</a><br />\n警再放催淚彈Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F471254926754367%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=67eaf285\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/471254926754367/</a><br />\n7.21 警察現場發放多枚催淚彈 22:20 Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F450544468858025%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e0266f25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/450544468858025/</a><br />\n速龍小隊斥記者「係咪中立、係咪有立場」Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F631475204017598%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=cd08f882\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/631475204017598/</a><br />\n【7.21 現場】警察防線前的媽媽 Stand News 立場新聞<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F679125395894103%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d1feac92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/679125395894103/</a><br />\n【721開槍實錄】 克警濫暴，我們必定會追究到底。 林鄭，請爲每滴港人流的血負責。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgodblesshk%2Fvideos%2F583308962199292%2F&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=a9d92ff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/godblesshk/videos/583308962199292/</a>"},{"pid":"18e35c9555ff84466dfbafa2880bd5f6655bac06","tid":1348172,"uid":143580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:57:52.000Z","msg":"piish"},{"pid":"cc638893a940a250bdf87a8ca17551e23f1e0ad2","tid":1348172,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:26:55.000Z","msg":"推得幾多得幾多"},{"pid":"4b2321cb2619fe2d2771a5181ccb422b1e2148f1","tid":1348172,"uid":36592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:01:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">為721上環抗爭正名：光復香港，時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"af71b8b72a2283d52b2f12b5f8835696827df011","tid":1348172,"uid":169771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a44a96878756b68c6e9d01145097c64d8d7cb20","tid":1348172,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:25:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a9aadf2a0cc52fbd5f8f9ef9bf63196dbaf84bf2","tid":1348172,"uid":2689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:55:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2943f7a4ba9138df89b51de976f65612dfed492a","tid":1348172,"uid":281533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T09:55:22.000Z","msg":"Pish