"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T13:19:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"169633b791ab76340f68dcfae6e9e8011ea2e2f6","tid":1348172,"uid":276191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T15:37:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9807cd868f442d459143adcf349cd900db5dfe0c","tid":1348172,"uid":272530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:02:45.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"ac41f1777e925d1f79c74db0082d73c1effbda70","tid":1348172,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T16:23:59.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"e27ea9945f5272eae99605be64040d5dc42f10fe","tid":1348172,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8feb38e432a32c0f7e186626f672d02daeae4212","tid":1348172,"uid":199709,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T07:56:59.000Z","msg":"上環Video 整合 (粗略)<br />\n<br />\n【721回顧 | 警察先主動進攻 狂射催淚彈橡膠彈】 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D341910530087022&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=778c3d78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=341910530087022</a><br />\n23:34 於永安中心外，示威者呼籲全部人「一齊走」。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D347322312837536&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=42a2d5e0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=347322312837536</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:44 警察向示威者開槍。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D336543320631999&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=9052eb71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=336543320631999</a><br />\n【721即時】22:38 在示威者推進途中，警方突然向人群射出催淚彈，及急速推進。示威者向警方投擲雜物還擊，警方再發射多枚催淚彈。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D436610810398685&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=dcccd9c6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=436610810398685</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:12 港澳碼頭外，警察向示威者施放胡椒噴霧。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D497139927720468&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=947aef02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=497139927720468</a><br />\n【721即時】 22:00 干諾道西港澳碼頭外警察突然推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2450364665024731&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=f762edfa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2450364665024731</a><br />\n21:20 警察以「一二一二」的口令由德輔道西向西邊街推進。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D1310939165740421&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=b7e51808\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=1310939165740421</a><br />\n20:55 中區警署外的示威者向警署外牆掉油漆彈、磚頭及腐蝕性液體 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D725595331211578&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=d196eb13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=725595331211578</a><br />\n20:23 有一批全black bloc的警員不斷推進防線，惟沒有委任證及證明文件。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D406909290170265&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=88223482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=406909290170265</a><br />\n20:13 示威者現正由干諾道西向後奔跑至德輔道西。 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D789204521474060&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=965f0302\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=789204521474060</a><br />\n<br />\n上環清場中 警方對這個用身體阻擋催淚彈的男人這樣處理<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAzZoteAvCyw&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=4c41c52e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzZoteAvCyw</a><br />\n示威者疑中槍倒地 同伴築防線助急救 <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D2433207320290299&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=0cae1002\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=2433207320290299</a><br />\n2019/0721/上環硝煙花特別多<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBpfKm3Ls34U%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=721b67db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BpfKm3Ls34U&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n2019/07/21上環。抗爭者心聲。他們有不想活的覺悟。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DS4OKmzwmhIo&d=9UH%2F9926htvwUrrmfnBdR4Znnstt8OVeiO3WagLZNiI%3D&h=e6d231f2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=S4OKmzwmhIo</a><br />\n黑警用橡膠子彈射頭<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/hk.nextmedia/videos/